How to have our AI assistant 
query openAI's GPT-3 and speak the result

Create openai account and get API key
https://openai.com/api/

Get API key
create .env file and add
OPENAI_API_KEY
OPENAI_ORG

Install openAI 
  pip3 install --upgrade openai

Install dotenv to load API key from 
an environment file
  pip3 install python-dotenv

Create method to query openAI API

Add module to AI assistant to launch
openAI Query